{
  "id": "adv_group_tri_03_04",
  "title": "TRINITYAiLE 03 04",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "勝負の内容はダンスバトルよ\nインターバルを挟みつつ三曲分",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The competition will be a dance battle.\nThree songs‚ with breaks in between.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 6.110340213775634,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 6.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "勝敗はその合計点で決める……ね\n了解。こっちはいつでも準備出来てます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We’ll decide the winner based on the total score… Right?\nGot it. I’m ready anytime.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.3,
      "endTime": 15.207550621032716,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10809.289606089389,
          "startTime": 17.10928960608939
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 11.578261014943333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 15.395956272756061
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "うん\nそれじゃあ……曲、流すね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay.\nI’ll… put on the music.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.395956272756061,
      "endTime": 19.44595627275606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 19.66262293942273
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "（瑠依ちゃん本気や、勝てば解散やのに……）\n（手抜かんつもりや。ほんまに強いな、覚悟が違うわ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Rui-chan is serious‚ we’ll disband if she wins…)\n(She’s not going to hold back. She’s really strong‚ her resolve is different.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.66262293942273,
      "endTime": 30.479335128143433,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 24.319717588027366
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 31.695956272756067
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……一曲目から飛ばし過ぎなんと違う？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whew… Don’t you think we’re going a bit too hard for the first song?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.99595627275607,
      "endTime": 38.25516285387179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 38.45516285387175
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことない\nむしろ、優こそ全然本気じゃないわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s not true.\nYou’re the one who’s not being serious at all‚ Yu.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.45516285387179,
      "endTime": 43.4150496908774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 43.62182952053845
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "まさか。これがうちの本気……全力なんやって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t be ridiculous. This is my true ability… I’m giving it my all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.62182952053845,
      "endTime": 49.040831862762566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 49.24083186276257
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "またそうやって、心にもないことを……\n私のためって言うのも、単なる嘘なのね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re saying that again‚ when you don’t even mean it…\nAnd saying it’s for my sake is just a lie too‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.24083186276257,
      "endTime": 55.647362529113884,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 55.84736252911388
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それはちゃいます！\nうちが心から思ってる、本当のことや",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-That’s not true!\nThat’s what I truly believe‚ it’s the truth.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.84736252911388,
      "endTime": 61.48806553967296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 61.68069586244719
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "なら、今ここで、それを証明してみせて\n今のパフォーマンスじゃ全然伝わってこなかったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then prove it to me‚ here and now.\nYour current performance didn’t convey it at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.68069586244719,
      "endTime": 68.08069576707975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 68.2806958624472
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "……っ！　わ、分かりました\nすみれちゃん、はよ次の曲、流して",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ugh! O-Okay.\nSumire-chan‚ hurry up and put on the next song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.2806958624472,
      "endTime": 74.83811068025726,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 71.41402919578059
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 75.03811068025728
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "あ……う、うん！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… O-Okay!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.03811068025728,
      "endTime": 76.90060495821137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 77.73811068025728
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "（すごい……優ちゃん、さっきより動きが良くなった）\n（瑠依ちゃんにあんなこと言われた……から？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Amazing… Yu-chan’s movements have gotten better.)\n(Is it because… Rui-chan said those things to her?)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.40477734692394,
      "endTime": 87.97924481518565,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 88.17144401359062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、瑠依ちゃんもますます切れが良くなったみたい）\n（これが瑠依ちゃんの……全力……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But Rui-chan’s movements are getting sharper too.)\n(This is Rui-chan’s… full potential…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.17144401359062,
      "endTime": 95.52713573264579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 95.73811068025732
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……まだ本気を出さないつもり？\nこのままなら、私が勝ってしまうわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huff‚ huff… Are you still not going to give it your all?\nIf you keep this up‚ I’m going to win.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.73811068025732,
      "endTime": 103.44493622270727,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 103.63811068025727
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "それとも……あなたの言う私やトリエルへの\n想いっていうのは、その程度ってこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Or… Is that all your feelings\nfor me and TRINITYAiLE amount to?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.63811068025727,
      "endTime": 110.23811087099214,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 110.4381106802573
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんな言い方……せんといて……！\n何度でも言うけど、想ってるんは本当やって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "D-Don’t say it like that…!\nI’ve told you over and over again that my feelings are real!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.4381106802573,
      "endTime": 118.6219202467551,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 118.81144403413131
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "うちなりに、どうしたら瑠依ちゃんやトリエルが\n輝けるかって、いつも全力で頭使ってたんよ……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve been using my brain to the fullest‚ trying to figure out\nhow to make Rui-chan and TRINITYAiLE shine…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.81144403413131,
      "endTime": 126.14849618867234,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 126.34849618867234
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "そう……でもそっちに気が回り過ぎて\nパフォーマンスの質を落としていたら、本末転倒よね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… But if you’re so focused on those things\nthat it lowers the quality of your performance‚ then you’re putting the cart before the horse.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.34849618867234,
      "endTime": 133.7878384967168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 133.98182952200563
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "私のためを想うなら、そんなことに精を出すより……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you’re thinking of me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.98182952200563,
      "endTime": 137.93867747580205,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 138.13867747580204
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04/sud_vo_adv_group_tri_03_04-rui009.m4a",
      "text": "自分のパフォーマンスに、本気を出してみせなさい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…put your heart into your performance!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.13867747580204,
      "endTime": 141.4154574135462,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 141.61545741354618
    },
    {
